name: Frontier Airlines Airbus A320neo Arrival and Departure at Calgary Airport
description:
Great to see the A320neo back here in Calgary! As one of the largest operators of the neo in North America with 10 neos in the fleet (at the time of uploading), it was inevitable that Calgary would see some of these birds on Frontier's first international route. Here we have N310FR, otherwise known as Sunny The Collared Lizard, arriving on 17L and then taxiing up close for departure again on 17L for Denver. ATC is included, enjoy this colourful neo!

Thanks for watching!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

FLIGHT INFORMATION
Airline: Frontier Airlines (FFT/F9)
Aircraft: Airbus A320-251N (A20N)
Flight Number: F9107/106
Aircraft Name: Sunny The Collared Lizard
Livery: New (2014) 
Engines: 2x CFMI LEAP-1A26 
Registration: N310FR
Route: Denver (DEN) - Calgary (YYC) - Denver (DEN)
Callsign: FRONTIER FLIGHT 107/106
Runway used: 17L
Date filmed: June 3rd, 2018
